{"TopicId":119756,"ForumId":44,"TopicTitle":"\u0026quot;Seas Of Infinity\u0026quot;, a bit of history that lead to space based telescopes.","CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-30T18:06:44Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"sal_vager","CreatedById":16426,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-30T18:06:44Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EA friend of mine showed me this today, it\u0027s a film from 1966 putting forward the case for orbital telescopes, which lead to the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Orbiting_Astronomical_Observatory\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EOrbiting Astronomical Observatory\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, which in turn lead to \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hubble_Space_Telescope\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EHubble\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E, and the \u003Ca href=\u0022https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/James_Webb_Space_Telescope\u0022 rel=\u0022external nofollow\u0022\u003E\u003Cstrong\u003EJames Webb Telescope.\u003C/strong\u003E\u003C/a\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cdiv class=\u0022ipsEmbeddedVideo \u0022 contenteditable=\u0022false\u0022\u003E\u003Cdiv\u003E\u003Ciframe width=\u0022459\u0022 height=\u0022344\u0022 src=\u0022https://www.youtube.com/embed/Kg1Um3rk65w?feature=oembed\u0022 frameborder=\u00220\u0022 allowfullscreen=\u0022true\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003C/div\u003E\u003Cp\u003ESome older members might recognise the name of the second astronomer in this presentation.\u003C/p\u003E\u003Cp\u003EIf it hadn\u0027t been for people like these advocating for space based science, Hubble and the ISS may never have happened.\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Capt\u0026#039;n Skunky","CreatedById":1261,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-30T18:27:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cimg src=\u0022http://i.imgur.com/RdN3r.png\u0022 alt=\u0022RdN3r.png\u0022\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"LordFerret","CreatedById":111598,"CreatedDateTime":"2015-08-30T18:46:28Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003EI remember watching this a long, long, long time ago.\u003C/p\u003E\n"}]}